From b144f89545a52941e8c421dadbb32c7f0bd9cb07 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Anthony Koo <Anthony.Koo@amd.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Sep 2019 10:52:15 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 1376/4530] drm/amd/display: correctly populate dpp refclk in
 fpga

[Why]
In diags environment we are not programming the DPP DTO
correctly.

[How]
Populate the dpp refclk in dccg so it can be used to correctly
program DPP DTO.

Signed-off-by: Anthony Koo <Anthony.Koo@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Tony Cheng <Tony.Cheng@amd.com>
Acked-by: Leo Li <sunpeng.li@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
---
